2017年'''東阿勒頗攻勢'''（{{lang-ar|هجوم شرق حلب}}）是[[敘利亞|敘利亞]]政府軍於2017年1月17日<ref name="jan17"/>發起的軍事行動，目的是攻佔[[伊斯兰国|伊斯兰国]]在[[阿勒颇省|阿勒颇省]]的僅餘控制區，阻止[[土耳其|土耳其]]支持的[[叙利亚反对派|叙利亚反对派]]在阿勒颇省東部推進，同時控制供應[[阿勒颇|阿勒颇]]市用水的水源。<ref name="cut off Turkish Army">{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-cutoff-turkish-army-southeast-aleppo-map/|title=Syrian Army to cutoff Turkish Army from southeast Aleppo: map|first=Leith|last=Fadel|date=19 February 2017|publisher=|access-date=2017-03-02|archive-date=2018-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181117031245/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-cutoff-turkish-army-southeast-aleppo-map/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=against>{{cite web|url=http://af.reuters.com/article/worldNews/idAFKBN1650AB|title=Syrian army advances against Islamic State near Aleppo - monitor|publisher=|access-date=2017-03-02|archive-date=2018-08-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180824101919/https://af.reuters.com/article/worldNews/idAFKBN1650AB|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.breitbart.com/news/army-presses-is-in-north-syria-monitor-military-source/|title=Army presses IS in north Syria: monitor, military source - Breitbart|publisher=|access-date=2017-03-02|archive-date=2019-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190203202040/https://www.breitbart.com/news/army-presses-is-in-north-syria-monitor-military-source/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==攻勢==
2017年1月17日，敘政府軍在[[巴卜|巴卜]]以南向伊斯蘭國發起攻勢。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://southfront.org/syrian-army-makes-first-gains-anti-isis-operation-south-al-bab|title=Syrian Army Makes First Gains In Anti-ISIS Operation South Of Al-Bab|date=18 January 2017|publisher=|access-date=2017-03-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170601130455/https://southfront.org/syrian-army-makes-first-gains-anti-isis-operation-south-al-bab/|archive-date=2017-06-01|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

在敘政府軍於2017年2月10日推進至距離[[巴卜|巴卜]]市不到2公里處後，<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/2017/02/kremlin-turkey-gave-target-mistaken-syria-strike-170210135054884.html|title=Kremlin: Turkey gave target for mistaken Syria strike|date=10 February 2017|access-date=10 February 2017|publisher=Al Jazeera|archive-date=2019-04-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190428165439/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2017/02/kremlin-turkey-gave-target-mistaken-syria-strike-170210135054884.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>據報土耳其支持的敘反對派在2月11日攻佔巴卜以南的一個具戰略價值的迴旋處，意味敘政府軍無法在不與反對派部隊交戰的情況下繼續向巴卜推進。敘利亞當局為阻止反對派部隊繼續向南深入，決定向Kuweires空軍基地以東的伊斯蘭國控制區進攻，以阻斷反對派南下之路。

2月12日至16日間，敘政府軍攻佔在Kuweires空軍基地東北方的9個村莊，距離伊斯蘭國控制的[[代爾哈菲爾|代爾哈菲爾]]（Dayr Hafir）鎮不到5公里。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.syriahr.com/en/?p=60936 |title=The regime forces are about 5 km northwest of Deir Hafer town after controlling 9 villages in the road between it and between al-Bab area |access-date=2017-03-02 |archive-date=2019-12-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191230114706/http://www.syriahr.com/en/?p=60936 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2月21日至25日間，敘軍再收復十餘個村莊，<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.syriahr.com/en/?p=61567 |title=The regime forces achieved a broad advancement in the road of al-Bab – al-Tabaqa and move towards al-Khafseh area |access-date=2017-03-02 |archive-date=2019-12-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191228023356/http://www.syriahr.com/en/?p=61567 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=ontherun>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/isis-run-syrian-army-liberates-two-villages-eastern-aleppo/|title=ISIS on the run as the Syrian Army liberates two more villages in eastern Aleppo|first=Chris|last=Tomson|date=24 February 2017|publisher=|access-date=2017-03-02|archive-date=2017-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171022193216/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/isis-run-syrian-army-liberates-two-villages-eastern-aleppo/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/busy-day-in-east-aleppo-as-syrian-army-obliterates-isis/|title=Busy day in East Aleppo as Syrian Army obliterates ISIS|first=Paul|last=Antonopoulos|date=25 February 2017|publisher=|access-date=2017-03-02|archive-date=2021-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210121012418/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/busy-day-in-east-aleppo-as-syrian-army-obliterates-isis/|dead-url=no}}</ref>代爾哈菲爾已處於敘軍炮火控制範圍之內。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/tiger-forces-liberate-new-village-isis-east-aleppo-map/|title=Tiger Forces liberate new village from ISIS in east Aleppo: map|first=Leith|last=Fadel|date=24 February 2017|publisher=|access-date=2017-03-02|archive-date=2017-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171022195025/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/tiger-forces-liberate-new-village-isis-east-aleppo-map/|dead-url=no}}</ref>由於伊斯蘭國在代爾哈菲爾可能設置了大量的防禦工事，敘軍不強攻代爾哈菲爾，繞過它繼續向東推進。<ref name=ontherun/>

在土耳其支持的敘反對派[[巴卜之戰|攻佔巴卜]]後，據守巴卜以南的塔代夫（Tadef）鎮的伊斯蘭國分子已有大部分撤出。2月26日，敘軍進入塔代夫並控制該鎮。<ref name=against/><ref name="Tadef liberated">{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/breaking-syrian-army-liberates-isis-held-town-neighboring-al-bab/|title=BREAKING: Syrian Army liberates ISIS-held town neighboring Al-Bab|first=Chris|last=Tomson|date=26 February 2017|publisher=|access-date=2017-03-02|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308095147/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/breaking-syrian-army-liberates-isis-held-town-neighboring-al-bab/|dead-url=no}}</ref>隨後敘政府軍與反對派部隊在塔代夫附近爆發衝突。反對派宣稱打死至少22名政府軍士兵。<ref name="Rudaw">{{cite web|url=http://www.rudaw.net/english/middleeast/syria/27022017|title=Reports: Syrian rebels, loyalists clash south of al-Bab near Tedef|date=2017-02-27|publisher=Rudaw|access-date=2017-03-02|archive-date=2020-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200925154447/http://www.rudaw.net/english/middleeast/syria/27022017|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2月27日，敘政府軍再攻佔數個村莊，到達[[曼比季|曼比季]]的[[敘利亞民主力量|敘利亞民主力量]]控制區，反對派趁伊斯蘭國撤退，佔領了5個村莊。<ref name="vie">{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/field-report-syrian-army-turkish-backed-forces-vie-control-northern-syria-map-update/|title=Field Report: Syrian Army, Turkish-backed forces vie for control in northern Syria. Map Update|first=Zen|last=Adra|date=2017-02-27|publisher=|access-date=2017-03-02|archive-date=2018-11-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181118155226/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/field-report-syrian-army-turkish-backed-forces-vie-control-northern-syria-map-update/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.syriahr.com/en/?p=61754 |title=-{The “Islamic State” organization withdraws from 23 villages east of al-Bab city and the regime forces finish drawing their border with the “Euphrates Shield” operation according to the Turkish – Russian agreement}- |access-date=2017-03-02 |archive-date=2019-12-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191228141417/http://www.syriahr.com/en/?p=61754 |dead-url=no }}</ref>敘利亞民主力量隨後向曼比季西南和以南的伊斯蘭國分子進攻，攻佔9個村莊。<ref name="restart">{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/massive-gains-isis-kurdish-troops-restart-operations-south-manbij/|title=Massive loss for ISIS as Kurdish troops restart operations south of Manbij|first=Chris|last=Tomson|date=2017-02-27|publisher=|access-date=2017-03-02|archive-date=2018-07-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180706193850/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/massive-gains-isis-kurdish-troops-restart-operations-south-manbij/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2月28日，土耳其支持的反對派部隊在Arima附近攻擊敘利亞民主力量，奪取了2個村莊。<ref name="3_villages"/><ref>{{cite web|url=https://southfront.org/pro-turkish-forces-seize-village-ypg-west-manbij-syrian-army-liberates-areas-isis/|title=Pro-Turkish forces seize village from YPG west of Manbij. Syrian Army liberates more areas from ISIS|publisher=South Front|date=2017-03-01|access-date=2017-03-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170708004041/https://southfront.org/pro-turkish-forces-seize-village-ypg-west-manbij-syrian-army-liberates-areas-isis/|archive-date=2017-07-08|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

3月1日，敘民主力量從伊斯蘭國手上攻佔5個村莊，<ref name="push">{{Cite web |url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/turkish-army-seizes-two-villages-kurdish-forces-amid-push-towards-manbij/ |title=Turkish Army seizes two villages from Kurdish forces amid push towards Manbij |access-date=2017-03-02 |archive-date=2017-08-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170830161933/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/turkish-army-seizes-two-villages-kurdish-forces-amid-push-towards-manbij/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>敘政府軍攻佔1個村莊。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/isis-run-east-aleppo-syrian-army-liberates-territory/ |title=ISIS on the run in east Aleppo as the Syrian Army liberates more territory |access-date=2017-03-02 |archive-date=2018-11-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181122193144/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/isis-run-east-aleppo-syrian-army-liberates-territory/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>敘反對派向[[曼比季|曼比季]]進軍，<ref name="push"/>攻佔3個原由敘民主力量控制的村莊。<ref name="3villages">{{Cite web |url=http://www.syriahr.com/en/?p=61944 |title=Rebels advance over Menbej military council in 3 villages |access-date=2017-03-02 |archive-date=2019-12-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191228044349/http://www.syriahr.com/en/?p=61944 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

