3月6日，敘政府軍從伊斯蘭國手上收復6個村莊。<ref name="6villages">{{Cite web |url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/six-villages-liberated-eastern-aleppo-syrian-army-closes-jarrah-airbase/ |title=Six villages liberated in eastern Aleppo as the Syrian Army closes in on Jarrah Airbase |access-date=2017-03-08 |archive-date=2019-12-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191230054549/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/six-villages-liberated-eastern-aleppo-syrian-army-closes-jarrah-airbase/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>3月7日，敘政府軍攻佔[[幼发拉底河|幼发拉底河]]西岸al-Khafsa的一個主要抽水站，該抽水站主要負責向[[阿勒颇|阿勒颇]]市供水，自從伊斯蘭國在多個星期前截斷供水後，阿勒頗市就陷入供水緊張。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.voanews.com/a/syrian-forces-capture-key-water-supply-aleppo-monitors-say/3754297.html |title=Monitors: Syrian Forces Capture Key Water Supply Near Aleppo |date=2017-03-07 |publisher=美國之音 |accessdate=2017-03-08 |archive-date=2019-06-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190606032211/https://www.voanews.com/a/syrian-forces-capture-key-water-supply-aleppo-monitors-say/3754297.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>同日敘軍[[老虎部隊|老虎部隊]]從伊斯蘭國手上收復另外23個村莊。<ref name=jan17>{{Cite web |url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/20-villages-liberated-syrian-army-seizes-isis-pocket-stunning-aleppo-offensive/ |title=+20 villages liberated as the Syrian Army seizes ISIS pocket in stunning Aleppo offensive |date=2017-03-07 |work=Al Masdar News |access-date=2017-03-08 |archive-date=2019-12-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191227093057/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/20-villages-liberated-syrian-army-seizes-isis-pocket-stunning-aleppo-offensive/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>3月8日敘軍收復另外21個村莊，並控制幼發拉底河另一個抽水站。<ref name="8villages">{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/photos-another-amazing-day-syrian-army-isis-faces-full-annihilation-rural-aleppo/|title=PHOTOS: Another amazing day for the Syrian Army as ISIS faces full annihilation in rural Aleppo|first=Paul|last=Antonopoulos|date=2017-03-08|publisher=|accessdate=2017-03-11|archive-date=2017-07-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170718161714/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/photos-another-amazing-day-syrian-army-isis-faces-full-annihilation-rural-aleppo/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-seizes-control-21-settlements-24-hours/|title=Syrian Army seizes control of 21 settlements in 24 hours|first=News|last=Desk|date=2017-03-09|publisher=|accessdate=2017-03-11|archive-date=2020-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200809141831/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-seizes-control-21-settlements-24-hours/|dead-url=no}}</ref>3月9日敘軍開始進攻吉拉赫（Jirah）空軍基地，<ref name="Jirah">{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-brink-liberating-key-military-airport-east-aleppo/|title=Syrian Army on the brink of liberating key military airport in east Aleppo|first=Leith|last=Fadel|date=2017-03-09|publisher=|accessdate=2017-03-11|archive-date=2020-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200921073253/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-brink-liberating-key-military-airport-east-aleppo/|dead-url=no}}</ref>但是於3月10日受沙塵暴影響導致攻勢被擊退。

===進攻代爾哈菲爾===
因天氣欠佳，[[老虎部隊|老虎部隊]]放棄進攻吉拉赫空軍基地，把目標轉移至Kuweires空軍基地以東的村莊。2017年3月13日，敘軍收復Humaymah Al-Kabira村和Humaymah Al-Saghira村，距離代爾哈菲爾不到2公里。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/bad-weather-halts-syrian-army-operations-east-aleppo/|title=Bad weather halts Syrian Army operations in east Aleppo|last=Fadel|first=Leith|date=2017-03-13|work=Al-Masdar News|accessdate=2017-03-13|language=en|archive-date=2019-12-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191230073157/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/bad-weather-halts-syrian-army-operations-east-aleppo/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-opens-new-front-isis-east-aleppo/|title=Syrian Army opens new front against ISIS in east Aleppo|last=Fadel|first=Leith|date=2017-03-13|work=Al-Masdar News|accessdate=2017-03-13|language=en|archive-date=2019-12-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191230182029/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-opens-new-front-isis-east-aleppo/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="new_front">{{Cite web |url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-opens-new-front-isis-east-aleppo/ |title=Syrian Army opens new front against #ISIS in east Aleppo |access-date=2017-03-31 |archive-date=2019-12-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191230182029/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-opens-new-front-isis-east-aleppo/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="new_front2">{{Cite news|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-advances-2km-isils-last-aleppo-stronghold-map/|title=Syrian Army advances with 2km of ISIL's last Aleppo stronghold: map|last=Fadel|first=Leith|date=2017-03-13|work=Al-Masdar News|accessdate=2017-03-13|language=en|archive-date=2020-01-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200104223333/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-advances-2km-isils-last-aleppo-stronghold-map/|dead-url=no}}</ref>3月15日和16日，敘軍收復代爾哈菲爾附近的另外8至9個村莊。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/breaking-syrian-army-liberates-four-villages-eastern-aleppo-encircles-isis-bastion/|title=BREAKING: Syrian Army liberates four villages in eastern Aleppo, encircles ISIS bastion|last=Tomson|first=Chris|date=2017-03-14|work=Al-Masdar News|access-date=2017-03-15|archive-date=2019-12-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191229163145/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/breaking-syrian-army-liberates-four-villages-eastern-aleppo-encircles-isis-bastion/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="new_front3">{{cite web|url=http://www.syriahr.com/en/?p=62982|title=With the end of the second month of military operation… the regime forces advance in 9 villages in Deir Hafer area after being expelled from al-Jarrah airbase by the "Islamic State" organization|publisher=SOHR|date=2017-03-16|accessdate=2017-03-17|archive-date=2019-12-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191226104050/http://www.syriahr.com/en/?p=62982|dead-url=no}}</ref>

3月17日和18日，敘軍攻佔代爾哈菲爾附近的另外8個村莊和2個小山。<ref name="new_front5">{{Cite web |url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/map-update-syrian-army-tightens-nose-around-isis-east-aleppo/ |title=Map Update: Syrian Army tightens the nose around ISIS in east Aleppo |access-date=2017-03-31 |archive-date=2020-05-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200518131144/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/map-update-syrian-army-tightens-nose-around-isis-east-aleppo/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://southfront.org/govt-forces-captures-strategic-hill-gets-fire-control-of-isis-held-city-of-deir-hafer/|title=Govt. forces captures strategic hill, gets fire control of ISIS-held city of Deir Hafer|publisher=South Front|date=18 March 2017|accessdate=18 March 2017|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170830103838/https://southfront.org/govt-forces-captures-strategic-hill-gets-fire-control-of-isis-held-city-of-deir-hafer/|archive-date=2017-08-30|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.syriahr.com/en/?p=63093|title=Regime forces advance in 2 villages over IS and reach Der Hafir outskirts|publisher=SOHR|date=18 March 2017|accessdate=18 March 2017|archive-date=2019-12-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191230050152/http://www.syriahr.com/en/?p=63093|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.syriahr.com/en/?p=63080|title=The regime forces advance further in their attempt to turn around Deir Hafer town|publisher=SOHR|date=18 March 2017|accessdate=18 March 2017|archive-date=2020-01-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200102213147/http://www.syriahr.com/en/?p=63080|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-reaches-outskirts-isils-last-east-aleppo-stronghold-map/|title=Syrian Army reaches outskirts of ISIL’s last east Aleppo stronghold: map|publisher=Al-Masdar News|date=18 March 2017|accessdate=18 March 2017|archive-date=2020-01-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200101001228/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-reaches-outskirts-isils-last-east-aleppo-stronghold-map/|dead-url=no}}</ref>到3月20日，敘軍已接近切斷代爾哈菲爾與馬斯卡納（Maskanah）之間的主要道路。<ref name="new_front7">{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-attempts-encircle-isis-east-aleppo/|title=Syrian Army attempts to encircle ISIS in east Aleppo|first=Zen|last=Adra|publisher=Al-Masdar News|date=20 March 2017|accessdate=20 March 2017|archive-date=2019-12-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191228024858/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-attempts-encircle-isis-east-aleppo/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.syriahr.com/en/?p=63221|title=The regime forces almost close the main road between Deir Hafer and Maskanah which leads to the countryside of Al-Raqqah and Deir Ezzor|publisher=SOHR|date=20 March 2017|accessdate=20 March 2017|archive-date=2020-01-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200102213151/http://www.syriahr.com/en/?p=63221|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="new_front8">{{Cite news|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/isis-almost-trapped-deir-hafer-syrian-army-seizes-villages-rural-aleppo/|title=ISIS almost trapped in Deir Hafer as Syrian Army seizes more villages in rural Aleppo|last=Tomson|first=Chris|date=2017-03-20|work=Al-Masdar News|access-date=2017-03-20|language=en|archive-date=2020-01-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200102015825/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/isis-almost-trapped-deir-hafer-syrian-army-seizes-villages-rural-aleppo/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

3月21日，敘軍在代爾哈菲爾以南攻佔另外3個村莊。<ref name="new_front9">{{Cite web |url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/breaking-government-forces-recapture-new-villages-east-aleppo/ |title=Breaking: Government forces recapture new villages in east Aleppo |access-date=2017-03-31 |archive-date=2019-12-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191225182350/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/breaking-government-forces-recapture-new-villages-east-aleppo/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://southfront.org/tiger-forces-liberate-3-villages-from-isis-southeast-of-deir-hafer-map/|title=Tigwr Forces liberate 3 villages from ISIS southeast of Deir Hafer (map)|publisher=South Front|date=2017-03-21|accessdate=2017-03-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170830103454/https://southfront.org/tiger-forces-liberate-3-villages-from-isis-southeast-of-deir-hafer-map/|archive-date=2017-08-30|dead-url=yes}}</ref>到3月22日，敘軍已幾乎完全包圍代爾哈菲爾。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://southfront.org/syrian-army-encircles-isis-stronghold-of-deir-hafer/|title=Syrian Army encircles ISIS stronghold of Deir Hafer|date=2017-03-22|work=South Front|access-date=2017-03-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170818085811/https://southfront.org/syrian-army-encircles-isis-stronghold-of-deir-hafer/|archive-date=2017-08-18|dead-url=yes}}</ref>3月23日，敘軍攻佔代爾哈菲爾以東的3個村莊，完全包圍代爾哈菲爾。<ref name="no way out">{{Cite web |url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/no-way-deir-hafer-isil-syrian-army-troops-full-besiege-town/ |title=No way out of Deir Hafer for ISIL as Syrian Army troops full besiege town |access-date=2017-03-31 |archive-date=2020-01-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200102085934/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/no-way-deir-hafer-isil-syrian-army-troops-full-besiege-town/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="liberation">{{Cite web |url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-continues-routing-isis-rural-aleppo-deir-hafer-liberates-new-village/ |title=Syrian Army continues routing ISIS in rural Aleppo after Deir Hafer, liberates new village |access-date=2017-03-31 |archive-date=2020-11-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201124211638/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-continues-routing-isis-rural-aleppo-deir-hafer-liberates-new-village/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>伊斯蘭國分子在各處佈置大量[[簡易爆炸裝置|簡易爆炸裝置]]後撤離代爾哈菲爾。在城鎮入口的拆彈工作完成大部分後，敘政府軍於3月29日正式進駐代爾哈菲爾。<ref name="entered_Dayr Hafir">[https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/pictures-syrian-army-enters-deir-hafer-first-time/ In Pictures: Syrian Army enters Deir Hafer for the first time] {{Wayback|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/pictures-syrian-army-enters-deir-hafer-first-time/ |date=20210108195639 }}, 2017-03-29</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/us-mideast-crisis-syria-army-idUSKBN1702B0 |title=Syrian army captures Islamic State village near Aleppo |author=Angus McDowall |date=2017-03-29 |accessdate=2017-04-01 |publisher=Reuters |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112012051/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-mideast-crisis-syria-army-idUSKBN1702B0 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

敘政府軍隨後暫緩在阿勒頗省東部的進攻，以集中兵力應付反對派部隊在[[哈馬省|哈馬省]]的[[2017年哈馬攻勢|新攻勢]]。哈馬前線回復穩定後，敘軍於2017年5月發動[[馬斯卡納平原攻勢|馬斯卡納平原攻勢]]，再次向吉拉赫空軍基地進攻。

